reviewText: They are just as polite and some even have a Diefenbaker.Love that dog and Canadian actor Paul Gross.David Marciano being from New Jersey mightbe why he seemed like a real Chicago cop.I purchased Season One, Season two and Season Three.Season Three  also includes  Call of the Wild Part 1 & 2.The DVD ran good the picture was clear the sound good.I think,  you will get the same  shows if purchaseDue South the Ultimate Collection instead of buying3 separate packs.(might check it out)

Title: Due South

reviewText: More like a two for the presentation. Seriously who designed the menu on this thing. I could have done a better job years with the free software that came on my laptop. I hear the Canadian version is better? But this is the one I could get. I love the show even after all these years and only wish that it had lasted longer. The tv movie comes with it so don't buy that seperate. I paid about twenty, if could do it over I would have waited till it droped down to ten because the menu is terrible. I gave five stars because I can't bring myself to rate it lower just because who ever was in charge of transferring it over to DVD didn't know what they were doing.
Title: Due South
